# ── Local task tracking (agent notes) ────────────────────────────────
# Ignore the CONTENTS of tasks/ (not the directory itself): a `!/tasks/x`
# negation cannot re-include a file when the parent `/tasks/` dir is excluded,
# so `/tasks/*` is required for the todo.md/lessons.md negations to take effect.
/tasks/*
!/tasks/todo.md
!/tasks/lessons.md

